Next to the Fat Baby Ban Mian store in Cantine. Serves halal western food of decent quality.
Tried chicken chop with tomato pasta, the pasta was quite soft and overcooked, sauce quite watery, chicken is quite small but overall it tastes ok. It's not expensive so not expecting too much. Chicken chop with fries, mashed potato and raisin bun was slightly better.
